{
  "stem": "5103.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And as they were shooting, these two men started running like crazy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And as they were walking, she told me, don't look.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Don't do anything, and put your doll on your star.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Put your-- I had a little cloth doll.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I put my little cloth doll on my star, and she had a handbag, which she covered.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she said, keep walking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Don't look.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And as these men flew by, she said, don't run.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they kept running, and they were shot right there in front of us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it was frightening.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I, I, just-- my mother said, don't look, don't look.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Keep walking, keep walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I had my little cloth doll, and, you know, she told me, like, put your hand on your doll, and-- and we made it home.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But that's how I knew we were Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, with my grandfather, all I-- of course, I, I had contact with them while we were in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it, it was very scattered, because already things were happening so much.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my grandfather had-- they had a system where if they put people in hospital, especially Jewish men, they put-- they used to put on the hospital ward-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] what is it called?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I, I-- contagious diseases.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if they-- the Germans were very cowardly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were really cowards.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If they saw there was a sign of any kind of disease that they might get, they would be a little bit wary of going in.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, my grandfather had a mild heart attack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he had been, he'd been sent to hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I think that was the visit we had made to him when this happened with these men being shot.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we had contact, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
